            "title": "关闭系统更新",
            "date_published": "2023-03-19T18:53:51.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>1、同时按下键盘的 Win+R 键，在弹出的运行框内输入 services.msc 后点确定。</p>\n<p>​    <img data-src=\"https://image.wawacm.com/wawacdn/20230322010208.png\" alt=\"0\" /></p>\n<p>​    <img data-src=\"https://image.wawacm.com/wawacdn/20230322010127.png\" alt=\"0\" /></p>\n<p>2、在弹出的服务窗口中向下拖找到 Windows Update 并双击打开。</p>\n<p>​    <img data-src=\"https://image.wawacm.com/wawacdn/20230322010149.png\" alt=\"0\" /></p>\n<p>3、在弹出的窗口中点停止，再将启用类型点开改为禁用。再点开上面的恢复选项卡，将所有的失败操作改为无操作，全部改完后点确定，重启生效。</p>\n<p>​    <img data-src=\"https://image.wawacm.com/wawacdn/20230322010208.png\" alt=\"0\" /></p>\n",
